
Tutorial URL: https://coursetro.com/courses/12/Learn-Angular-4-from-Scratch

Development Set up
	Install AngularJS4
		1. Install Node
		2. Install npm package manager
		3. Install angular/cli
			> npm install -g @angular/cli
		4. Start cli
			> ng -v 
	TypeScript for Sublime
		- Clone git repo into sublime Package directory
		> cd ~/AppData/Roaming/Sublime\ Text\ 2/Packages/
		> git clone https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript-Sublime-Plugin.git 
